#, no-c-format
msgid "Authors"
msgstr "लेखकाः"

#. Tag: para
#: man-kdiff3.1.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "This manual page was written by &Burkhard.Lueck; &Burkhard.Lueck.mail;."
msgstr "इदं पुस्तिकापृष्ठं &Burkhard.Lueck; &बर्खार्ड.लुएक्.मेल;."
